snippet.title: Astro Trailer (Alpha) | Zero Gravity FPS
snippet.description:
https://discord.gg/HwMFGPzFZn

First Official Trailer for Astro! A zero gravity movement fps with fun physics and gunfights. Astro will be free to play on steam. Release date TBA.


Join our discord to engage in the growing Astro community where you can play Astro offline or with others through community hosted servers, suggest ideas to delgoodie, and follow development more closely to see the design and decision-making that goes into Astro!

 #gamedev #fps #trailer
